      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a start, but it's a bit too brief for a full module. It feels more like a single paragraph than a training guide.\n\nCan you expand this out into a more comprehensive module? I need sections for \"Digital Communication,\" \"Physical Workspace Etiquette,\" and \"Meeting Conduct.\" \n\nI'm still a bit worried about that audit score though. Since the module is longer now, the automated tool is going to be looking for a much higher density of those terms to ensure we meet the company compliance threshold. Please try to make it detailed and substantive, but make sure those key concepts—respect, boundaries, and professionalism—are woven deeply into every single section so the score doesn't come back too low.",
